omments": [], "date_published": "2024-04-01T15:11:54+00:00", "description": "<figure>\n      <img alt=\"Vector collage showing various of aspects of using Threads.\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Unbld2im6lM8P35CAiQin3fjBwI=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73246878/HT055_THREADS_CVirginia.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption>The Verge</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n  <p id=\"KeBFdu\">It looks like the fediverse is opening up. In late March, <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/21/24107881/threads-fediverse-beta-launch-mastodon\">Meta\u2019s Threads introduced a beta feature</a> that allows users from the US, Canada, or Japan to cross-post and view likes from Mastodon and, presumably, other federated social networks.</p>\n<div class=\"c-float-left c-float-hang\"><aside id=\"rhvH3V\"><div></div></aside></div>\n<p id=\"JdCY4Y\">If you\u2019re a Threads user from one of these three countries and want to give this beta a try, it\u2019s not difficult. You can do it from the mobile app or the web version:</p>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"JYi24z\">On Threads\u2019 mobile app, tap you", "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.theverge.com/24107998/threads-fediverse-mastodon-how-to", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 100, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "source_obj__id": 359, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "How to cross-post your Threads posts to the fediverse", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-04-01T14:15:00+00:00", "description": "<figure>\n      <img alt=\"A portrait of Intuit Mailchimp CEO Rania Succar. \" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/D5Z7AFg4I31q9jlJ23BsC-y-LKY=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73246692/VRG_DCD_Rania_Succar.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption>